We chose to fit the data in a beta regression considering that the IDER score is conditionally distributed rather than Gaussian [26], meaning it is a continuous variable bounded between 10 and 40. To proceed the analysis we transformed the IDER scores to be between 0 and 1 using the following formula\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
